column_m = ["months", "cases", "genz", "mil", "geny", "boom", "nogen", "white", "black", "asian", "hispanic", "other", "norace"]
months = pd.DataFrame(columns = column_m)
month = '1'
year_m = '2005'
case_m = 0
kuka_m = []
for j in traffic['stop_date']:
    date = j.split('/')
    if len(date) == 3:
        if date[0] == month:
            case_m += 1
        else:
                row = {"months" : year_m+"/"+month, "cases" : case_m}
                months = months.append(row, ignore_index = True)
                row = {}
                case_m = 1
                month = date[0]
                year_m = date[2]
    else:
        kuka_m.append(j)
months = months.append({"months" : year_m+"/"+month, "cases" : case_m}, ignore_index = True)

yr = "2005"
mnth = "10"
genz = 0 # -25
mil = 0 # 26-41
geny = 0 # 42-57
boom = 0 # 58-
hanyadik = 8
for i in range(len(traffic)):
    date = traffic.loc[i, "stop_date"]
    age = traffic.loc[i, "driver_age"]
    if len(date.split("/")) == 3:
        if (date.split("/")[0] in ["1", "2", "3", "4", "5", "6", "7", "8", "9"] and date.split("/")[2] == "2005" ) or pd.isna(date):
            pass
        else:
            if date.split("/")[0] == mnth and date.split("/")[2] == yr:
                if age <= 25:
                    genz += 1
                elif age >= 26 and age <= 41:
                    mil += 1
                elif age >= 42 and age <= 57:
                    geny += 1
                elif age >= 58:
                    boom += 1

            else:
                months["genz"][hanyadik] = genz
                months["mil"][hanyadik] = mil
                months["geny"][hanyadik] = geny
                months["boom"][hanyadik] = boom
                months["nogen"][hanyadik] = months["cases"][hanyadik] - genz - geny - mil - boom
                
                hanyadik += 1
                mnth = date.split("/")[0]
                yr = date.split("/")[2]
                if age <= 25:
                    genz = 1
                    mil = 0
                    geny = 0
                    boom = 0
                elif age >= 26 and age <= 41:
                    genz = 0
                    mil = 1
                    geny = 0
                    boom = 0
                elif age >= 42 and age <= 57:
                    genz = 0
                    mil = 0
                    geny = 1
                    boom = 0
                elif age >= 58:
                    genz = 0
                    mil = 0
                    geny = 0
                    boom = 1 
                elif pd.isna(age):
                    genz = 0
                    mil = 0
                    geny = 0
                    boom = 0 
    else:
        pass

yr = "2005"
mnth = "10"
white = 0
black = 0
asian = 0
hisp = 0
other = 0
hanyadik = 8
for i in range(len(traffic)):
    date = traffic.loc[i, "stop_date"]
    color = traffic.loc[i, "driver_race"]
    if len(date.split("/")) == 3:
        if (date.split("/")[0] in ["1", "2", "3", "4", "5", "6", "7", "8", "9"] and date.split("/")[2] == "2005" ) or pd.isna(date):
            pass
        else:
            if date.split("/")[0] == mnth and date.split("/")[2] == yr:
                if color == "White":
                    white += 1
                elif color == "Black":
                    black += 1
                elif color == "Asian":
                    asian += 1
                elif color == "Hispanic":
                    hisp += 1
                elif color == "Other":
                    other += 1

            else:
                months["white"][hanyadik] = white
                months["black"][hanyadik] = black
                months["asian"][hanyadik] = asian
                months["hispanic"][hanyadik] = hisp
                months["other"][hanyadik] = other
                months["norace"][hanyadik] = months["cases"][hanyadik] - white - black - asian - hisp - other
                
                hanyadik += 1
                mnth = date.split("/")[0]
                yr = date.split("/")[2]
                if color == "White":
                    white = 1
                    black = 0
                    asian = 0
                    hisp = 0
                    other = 0
                elif color == "Black":
                    white = 0
                    black = 1
                    asian = 0
                    hisp = 0
                    other = 0
                elif color == "Asian":
                    white = 0
                    black = 0
                    asian = 1
                    hisp = 0
                    other = 0
                elif color == "Hispanic":
                    white = 0
                    black = 0
                    asian = 0
                    hisp = 1
                    other = 0
                elif color == "Other":
                    white = 0
                    black = 0
                    asian = 0
                    hisp = 0
                    other = 1
                elif pd.isna(color):
                    white = 0
                    black = 0
                    asian = 0
                    hisp = 0
                    other = 0

    else:
        pass

yr = "2005"
mnth = "10"
honapszamolo = 0
a = 0
t = 0
for i in range(len(traffic)):
    date = traffic.loc[i, "stop_date"]
    age = traffic.loc[i, "driver_age"]
    time = traffic.loc[i, "stop_time"]
    if len(date.split("/")) == 3:
        if (date.split("/")[0] in ["1", "2", "3", "4", "5", "6", "7", "8", "9"] and date.split("/")[2] == "2005" ) or (date.split("/")[0] == "10" and date.split("/")[2] == "2011") or pd.isna(date):
            pass
        else:
            if date.split("/")[0] == mnth and date.split("/")[2] == yr:
                m = honapszamolo
                if age <= 25:
                    a = 0
                elif age >= 26 and age <= 41:
                    a = 1
                elif age >= 42 and age <= 57:
                    a = 2
                elif age >= 58:
                    a = 3
                t = int(time.split(":")[0])
                kor_ora[m][a][t] += 1
            else:
                mnth = date.split("/")[0]
                yr = date.split("/")[2]
                honapszamolo += 1
                m = honapszamolo
                if age <= 25:
                    a = 0
                elif age >= 26 and age <= 41:
                    a = 1
                elif age >= 42 and age <= 57:
                    a = 2
                elif age >= 58:
                    a = 3
                t = int(time.split(":")[0])
                kor_ora[m][a][t] += 1
    else:
        pass

let_bun = np.zeros((72, 2, 5)) # m - a - v
yr = "2005"
mnth = "10"
honapszamolo = 0
aa = 0
v = 0
for i in range(len(traffic)):
    date = traffic.loc[i, "stop_date"]
    violation = traffic.loc[i, "violation"]
    arrested = traffic.loc[i, "is_arrested"]
    if len(date.split("/")) == 3:
        if (date.split("/")[0] in ["1", "2", "3", "4", "5", "6", "7", "8", "9"] and date.split("/")[2] == "2005" ) or (date.split("/")[0] == "10" and date.split("/")[2] == "2011") or pd.isna(date):
            pass
        else:
            if date.split("/")[0] == mnth and date.split("/")[2] == yr:
                m = honapszamolo
                if arrested == True:
                    aa = 0
                elif arrested == False:
                    aa = 1
                if violation == "Speeding":
                    v = 0
                elif violation == "Other":
                    v = 4
                elif violation == "Equipment":
                    v = 1
                elif violation == "Moving violation":
                    v = 2
                elif violation == "Registration/plates":
                    v = 3
                let_bun[m][aa][v] += 1
            else:
                mnth = date.split("/")[0]
                yr = date.split("/")[2]
                honapszamolo += 1
                m = honapszamolo
                if arrested == True:
                    aa = 0
                elif arrested == False:
                    aa = 1
                if violation == "Speeding":
                    v = 0
                elif violation == "Other":
                    v = 4
                elif violation == "Equipment":
                    v = 1
                elif violation == "Moving violation":
                    v = 2
                elif violation == "Registration/plates":
                    v = 3
                let_bun[m][aa][v] += 1
    else:
        pass
